ecc-aws-018-iam_users_receive_permission:
IAM users are granted access to services, functions, and data through IAM policies. 
There are three ways to define policies for a user: 
1) edit the user policy directly (inline); 
2) attach the policy directly to a user; 
3) add the user to an IAM group that has the policy attached.Only the third implementation is recommended.

