aws sns create-topic --name <sns_topic_name>
5. Subscribe an endpoint to an Amazon SNS topic. If the endpoint type is HTTP/S or email, or if the endpoint and the topic are not in the same Amazon Web Services account, the endpoint owner must run the ConfirmSubscription action to confirm the subscription.
aws sns subscribe --topic-arn <sns_topic_arn>  --protocol email --notification-endpoint <sns_subscription_endpoints> 
